{"tid":119402,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[啪啪啪]《第一屆LIHKG中文打字大賽》現正接受報名！","createTime":"2017-02-13T17:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T17:11:28.000Z","uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c483a138f8dc8a18e23c442b2577f489e24bff8","tid":119402,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:02:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《第一屆高登中文打字大賽》<br />\n現正接受報名！</span></div><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打，我係 沙填入臀門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (既代言人)<br />\n<br />\n今次&amp;#22021;《高登中文打字大賽》會&amp;#21946; TypeRacer 進行<br />\n<br />\n比賽當晚會&amp;#21946; Twitch 進行直播，有巴打即場旁述 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重會有即場投注系統，俾各位巴打邊睇邊*落注！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/a5dd7bd953.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2Fa5dd7bd953.png&h=4d9ef830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比賽詳情：<br />\n<br />\n日期&amp;時間：現在<br />\n<br />\n場地：<a href=\"http://play.typeracer.com/?universe=lang_zh-tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplay.typeracer.com%2F%3Funiverse%3Dlang_zh-tw&d=QsQvn9KnS4zrnMXWGBKJeEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=1f1091bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://play.typeracer.com/?universe=lang_zh-tw</a><br />\n<br />\n直播：<a href=\"http://twitch.tv/smilesnooker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitch.tv%2Fsmilesnooker&d=QsQvn9KnS4zrnMXWGBKJeEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=1489028d\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitch.tv/smilesnooker</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參賽方法：<br />\n<br />\n1. 去 <a href=\"http://play.typeracer.com/?universe=lang_zh-tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplay.typeracer.com%2F%3Funiverse%3Dlang_zh-tw&d=QsQvn9KnS4zrnMXWGBKJeEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=1f1091bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://play.typeracer.com/?universe=lang_zh-tw</a> 註冊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">First Name 請用高登膠名，Last Name 不要填！</span> 例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/a5c04739e4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2Fa5c04739e4.png&h=d83872b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 在此Post回覆報名（必須留Twitch ID或Email，用作通知參賽者比賽網址）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">報名格式：<br />\n1. 高登膠名 (TypeRacerUserName) Twitch ID/Email</span><br />\n例子1：沙填入臀門 (hkgsandy) smilesnooker<br />\n例子2：沙填入臀門 (hkgsandy) hkgsandy@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n3. 留意比賽當晚公佈的賽程表，晚上十點準時出席<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比賽規則 同 賽程表 視乎參賽人數再作決定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想知最新比賽消息，敬請留意住呢個Post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想同各位巴打一齊大顯指頭，成為高登神之手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即刻報名參加啦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*比賽當晚，只提供虛擬貨幣『沙填入臀門股份』給大家下注 <br />\n絕不接受現金投注 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">沙填入臀門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkgsandy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkgsandy&d=QsQvn9KnS4zrnMXWGBKJeEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=aea0cd5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkgsandy</a></span><br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"69034539382fee06dd15d5c59f98fa643d65ac2d","tid":119402,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:07:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19dbe252269369b514b67206c0ce2f98054dd4d5","tid":119402,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"推"}]}